OL,3,CPuffin population in Skomer Island
OL,4,Csees a 'slight dip' in numbers
OL,6,FSkomer Island along the coastline is
OL,7,Fwell known as one of the UK's largest
OL,8,FPuffin colonies.
OL,10,FBut an annual count of the species'
OL,11,Fpopulation on the island has shown a
OL,12,Ffall in numbers.
OL,14,FThe number of puffins counted on
OL,15,FSkomer Island this year came to 41,605
OL,16,Fwhich is between 900 to 1,000 down on
OL,17,Flast year's population.
