OL,3,CPuffin population in Skomer Island
OL,4,Csees a 'slight dip' in numbers
OL,6,FRob Knott, Skomer Island's Visitor
OL,7,FOfficer said: "Last year's count of
OL,8,F42,500 was a record high, so a slight
OL,9,Fdip this year is not something to be
OL,10,Fconcerned about, particularly in light
OL,11,Fof the bad weather we've had over the
OL,12,Fpast few weeks.
OL,14,F"We've only had an opportunity to do
OL,15,Fone count, so we're taking it off that
OL,16,Fone number whereas we'd like to take
OL,17,Fit off 2 or 3 counts usually."
