OL,3,CPuffin population in Skomer Island
OL,4,Csees a 'slight dip' in numbers
OL,6,FAside from keeping count of the
OL,7,Fpuffins, the team on Skomer welcome
OL,8,Fover 250 visitors to the island every
OL,9,Fday, with 16 people also staying in
OL,10,Fthe hostel each night. That totals at
OL,11,Fmore than 20,000 visitors per year.
OL,13,FThe Wildlife Trust of South & West
OL,14,FWales has been working on a project to
OL,15,Fintroduce new webcams on the island
OL,16,Fwith the aim of ensuring that everyone
OL,17,Fcan access footage to see the variety
OL,18,Fof birds and species that live there.
