OL,3,CPuffin population in Skomer Island
OL,4,Csees a 'slight dip' in numbers
OL,6,FGrace Hunt, Fundraising &
OL,7,FCommunications Officer for the
OL,8,FWildlife Trust of South & West Wales
OL,9,Fadded: "We've got two cameras, one on
OL,10,Fthe bank which showcases all the
OL,11,Ffantastic wildlife we've got, so
OL,12,Fpuffins, rabbits, gulls, seabirds of
OL,13,Fall sorts, shapes and sizes.
OL,15,F"We've also got a burrow cam which is
OL,16,Fgoing to show the life cycle of the
OL,17,FManx shearwater which are nocturnal
OL,18,Fbirds that a lot of day visitors don't
OL,19,Fget to see."
